{"tid":348720,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"文頌嫻周家蔚姚樂怡帶仔女玩轉澳門 湯盈盈與錢七無影","createTime":"2017-08-06T03:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T08:17:46.000Z","uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"784d5ea6cad32b09505e2d8bab051143efa80a56","tid":348720,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/111233_02a51871ef3a517eabdf255a82768644.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F111233_02a51871ef3a517eabdf255a82768644.jpg&h=4c05c5cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/111428_0a80e951772245f1799f1429dbde0524.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F111428_0a80e951772245f1799f1429dbde0524.jpg&h=f5920c87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/111617_a865f92fb6c20f991ea5d2305dc5aae4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F111617_a865f92fb6c20f991ea5d2305dc5aae4.jpg&h=7930ef51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/111447_3091b9bee43ff41020498b843d8e9d62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F111447_3091b9bee43ff41020498b843d8e9d62.jpg&h=c862bed2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/111447_771b94fc0563289dc2ffd12b02159ac6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F111447_771b94fc0563289dc2ffd12b02159ac6.jpg&h=321a934a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/111448_771b94fc0563289dc2ffd12b02159ac6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F111448_771b94fc0563289dc2ffd12b02159ac6.jpg&h=ea97f6e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/111448_441f2f1056dbf1cef62bfd7bad1dd685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F111448_441f2f1056dbf1cef62bfd7bad1dd685.jpg&h=1217e519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藝人文頌嫻日前相約好友姚樂怡、周家蔚與洪天明，齊齊帶埋仔女到澳門新濠影滙玩餐飽！三家人除了到訪新濠影滙著名的景點影匯之星，坐8字形的摩天輪外，亦有到酒店的游泳池及室內遊樂場玩，更到大和夏祭市集，與一眾Sanrio卡通人物影靚相、歎美食！<br />\n<br />\n五歲囡囡吸黑力太強<br />\n<br />\n文頌嫻在社交網分享囡囡Jamie的游泳照，快五歲的Jamie穿上救生衣自己一個玩滑梯！她透過短訊向東網透露囡囡太黑，笑言熄燈後完全「消失」，她說：「囡囡之前去泰國曬得一身健康膚色，今次去澳門都有在酒店玩水上活動，即使做足防曬措施，但她吸黑力太強，晩上關了燈完全看不到她！」而好友姚樂怡亦與老公帶同一歲的囡囡「小雞髀」坐摩天輪，摩天輪初體驗的她表現淡定又興奮。<br />\n<br />\n洪天明做攝影師<br />\n<br />\n周家蔚則上載多張照片，見天明孭大背包、心口掛相機，準備充足為太太與仔仔影靚相。家蔚又在泳池抱起仔仔，玩得十分開心！她透露暑假已過一半，想與好友及小朋友到近一點的地方玩，澳門就是不錯的選擇，她說：「去市集最開心係細仔，佢好鍾意啲卡通人物。去埋酒店個室內遊樂場，我都陪兩個仔爬嚟爬去！」由於今次沒有帶女傭同行，故湊仔工作由她與天明分擔！"},{"pid":"6f6b28c5cb8e6896d156989f64d7d07e882f4141","tid":348720,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/111723_74fd24aa2bb458e125e90c734e3a281d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F111723_74fd24aa2bb458e125e90c734e3a281d.jpg&h=f72836c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"640bace3f06250bdbf43334699a16cdf3bbed8d1","tid":348720,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:23:33.000Z","msg":"文頌嫻結左婚都仲有仙氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8883ecf5e2969591fa682b75b01812ffe4e1b5cc","tid":348720,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:26:34.000Z","msg":"<blo